---
description: Commit Message Rules
alwaysApply: true
---
When generating commit messages (including the Changes tab button), strictly use:
- <type>(<scope>): <subject>
- Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, build, ci
- Subject ≤ 72 chars, imperative mood
Include a 1–3 line body when non-trivial.